    <stitle>9 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS INTERNATIONAL PS125-9A, PS140-9A, PSO125-9A, PSO140-9A AND PSO150-9A - CLEAN AND
        INSPECT - REMOTE CONTROL
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>REMOTE CONTROL</title>
        <para>Check the shift fingers, bushing bores and rods for excessive wear or scuffing. Replace springs, bearing
            races, boots and seals. Clean all reusable parts thoroughly and apply a light coat of grease to the pivot
            points when reassembling.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
